data.title: Albania Currency in Circulation: Annual: Banknotes: 200 LEK
data.meta_description: Albania Currency in Circulation: Annual: Banknotes: 200 LEK data was reported at 3,184.000 ALL mn in Dec 2022. This records an increase from the previous number of 3,112.000 ALL mn for Dec 2021. Albania Currency in Circulation: Annual: Banknotes: 200 LEK data is updated yearly, averaging 2,352.000 ALL mn (Median) from Dec 2004 to 2022, with 19 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 3,204.000 ALL mn in 2008 and a record low of 1,827.000 ALL mn in 2012. Albania Currency in Circulation: Annual: Banknotes: 200 LEK data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by Bank of Albania. The data is categorized under Global Database’s Albania – Table AL.KA002: Currency in Circulation.
